ivardefs.name: attachment
ivardefs.desc: The document or URL of the document along with critical metadata to prove content has integrity.

ivardefs.name: format
ivardefs.desc: An identifier of the document encoding, structure, and template that the document conforms to beyond the base format indicated in the mimeType.

properties.desc: The document and format referenced. There may be multiple content element repetitions, each with a different format.
